echo "Following the route. You come across a calm body of water. This appears to a surrounding tree landscape with no movement. You feel eerily calm, but no rush to leave. You scout out a lush garden to your right, an arch way directly infront of you and behind the lake, and to your right an unmarked path with dark vines and dead looking trees."
echo "Before deciding whether to continue on with any of these paths, you see the calm body of water start to move in one specific spot. You move closer to get a clearer view of the movement, but a head begins to slowly rise. A woman emerges."
