Option 1 (Deep Lake) echo "You proceed leftward as the lady told. You following along the side of the lake to a more dark blue area with a huge waterfall. There lays in the middle a stoneline mound with a rod pointed out. You carefully navigate towards it, without falling in to the surrounding water. Climbing up the mound, you notice a voice singing to you."
read -p "What do you do[notice or continue]:
Option continue echo "You proceed to continue to the top, keeping your determination. You see a sword upon the top with it inside the top of the stone. You try to pull it out, for which it gives way. When released. The singing halts to a stop. You turn towards the direction of where the signing happened, noting a fish-like woman's head staring at you. She then swims under the water as you look in confusion. You turn to look at the sword and read the word 'Excalibur' engraved on the side. You head down the mound and travel back to the original part of the lake. 
Option notice echo "You turn to see a fish-like human being, staring at you. You feel the urgue to head towards her. But as soon as you take one step down towards her, a hand grabs your ankle as a terrifying his comes from below. You startle and look down to see a menacing physique of a similar creature with a hand grasp on, hissing and preparing to bite your foot with razor sharp teeth. You yank your foot back and glance quickly around to see multiple mermaids coming towards you. You quickly climb the mound to get higher ground, seeing the sword in a stone. You quickly try pulling it out, to which is slides out smoothly. The creatures all hiss at you as you aim it in their directions. They all leave in fear as you stand their in suprise. You look at the sword and see the engraving on the side 'Excalibur'. You quickly hop down the mound and sprint back to the lake."
